value.0: This corpse probably belongs to an elf. The upper part of his body disappears under a boulder and is therefore hard to identify, but the skinny legs are a solid hint.
An indecipherable message is scrawled on the tombside in fresh blood. You wonder what undead lord calls this sarcophagus his home.
A strong rope made from hemp, dangling from some place above you.
The stone lid is heavy, designed as much to keep thieves out as to keep the dead entombed within.
